{"tid":1504824,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪唔應該再申請不反對通知書？","createTime":"2019-08-25T11:48:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T14:31:47.000Z","uid":306738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b8a4eba6d6d4571e0d461fd4f4e1d6a49ccd08dd","tid":1504824,"uid":306738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:48:59.000Z","msg":"P牌第一次出post<br />\n<br />\n申請唔申請 都會有人出 <br />\n例如 各區居民即時落街 香港之路 和理飛 百步梯 <br />\n只要要夠宣傳 有一條大概路線 同共識既和理非時間<br />\n(即等一家大細走晒既時間） <br />\n<br />\n宜加有無不反對通知書都會告你非法集結 好似觀塘搞手咁<br />\n只要無大台 無有名有姓既搞手 <br />\n無人同黑警傾 亦無人係名義上負責任<br />\n仲可以睇成市民已視不反對通知書如無物<br />\n<br />\n相反 係有反對通知書之下 黨鐵可以大條道理預先封站<br />\n雖然無佢都可以即刻停你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜加無地鐵真係好難走"},{"pid":"b9a8970e17a377f2161feef36210f2e09e7f1102","tid":1504824,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:51:17.000Z","msg":"仲要捉撚埋個搞手先最慘"},{"pid":"a4084c0ecda5d8b6debce20cbc0fb5eba2e2bdb5","tid":1504824,"uid":74958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:52:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b5d177a52c4c8f2d0637af3ab402ef2022897852","tid":1504824,"uid":306738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9a8970e17a377f2161feef36210f2e09e7f1102","tid":1504824,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:51:17.000Z","msg":"仲要捉撚埋個搞手先最慘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:54:57.000Z","msg":"宜加係唔係都捉 根本唔理有無證據"},{"pid":"70367c751a0fa436af6361448e0026a38bfcdce6","tid":1504824,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T14:28:43.000Z","msg":"申請被拒批，都係一種宣傳"},{"pid":"773baca38a894a88ff4215bac9284a1ae90f24c4","tid":1504824,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T14:31:47.000Z","msg":"申, 日日申, 唔同人, 一人一次, 大把人可以申<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多到佢做唔切, 就去嗰個, stress test 佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj